  ---
  E-Fence: Databricks Lakeflow Architecture

  Wi-Fi and Bluetooth Ingest — Implementation Reference

  ---
  1. Executive Architecture Summary

  E-Fence ingests RF observations from Raspberry Pi edge sensors into Databricks via two completely independent Lakeflow Declarative Pipeline flows — one for Wi-Fi, one for
  Bluetooth. Each flow has its own landing volume, bronze streaming table, and silver normalization table. They share a gold analytics layer where cross-protocol correlation,
  co-presence detection, and threat scoring occur.

  End-to-end flow:

  Raspberry Pi Sensor
       │ JSON over HTTPS/SFTP/MQTT-bridge
       ▼
  Unity Catalog Volume (landing zone)
    /Volumes/efence/wifi_raw/landing/       ← Wi-Fi JSON files
    /Volumes/efence/bt_raw/landing/         ← BT JSON files
       │
       ▼ Auto Loader (cloudFiles)
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │ Pipeline 1: efence-wifi-ingest  (DLT)                   │
  │  efence.wifi_raw.observations_bronze  (append-only)     │
  │  efence.wifi_silver.observations      (normalized)      │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │ Pipeline 2: efence-bluetooth-ingest (DLT)               │
  │  efence.bt_raw.observations_bronze    (append-only)     │
  │  efence.bt_silver.observations        (normalized)      │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
       │
       ▼ spark.readStream.table() (cross-pipeline)
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │ Pipeline 3: efence-gold-analytics   (DLT)               │
  │  efence.gold.device_timeline                            │
  │  efence.gold.copresence_events                          │
  │  efence.gold.perimeter_alerts                           │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
       │
       ▼
  Databricks SQL / BI / ML / Alert Systems

  Technology choices:
  - Lakeflow Declarative Pipelines (DLT) for all pipeline logic — declarative expectations, lineage, auto-restart
  - Auto Loader with cloudFiles.format=json for edge-to-cloud ingest
  - Delta for all tables; append-only bronze with pipelines.reset.allowed=false
  - Unity Catalog three-level namespace for governance, lineage, and ACL
  - Lakeflow Jobs (Workflows) for orchestration: 5-minute micro-batch trigger, daily maintenance
  - Databricks Secrets for the MAC hash salt — never in code or config plaintext

