  6. Data Quality and Governance

  Expectation tiers

  ┌───────────┬─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │   Tier    │    DLT decorator    │                       Behavior                        │
  ├───────────┼─────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ Hard drop │ @dlt.expect_or_drop │ Row dropped; tracked in DLT event log                 │
  ├───────────┼─────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ Warn      │ @dlt.expect         │ Row passes; metric incremented                        │
  ├───────────┼─────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ Fail      │ @dlt.expect_or_fail │ Pipeline halts (use only for catastrophic violations) │
  └───────────┴─────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  Bronze expectations (warn only — preserve everything)

  - valid_sensor_id: sensor_id IS NOT NULL AND LENGTH(sensor_id) > 0
  - valid_event_time: event_time IS NOT NULL
  - event_not_future (drop): event_time <= current_timestamp() + INTERVAL 5 MINUTES

  Silver expectations (drop invalid rows)

  - valid_event_id (drop): event_id IS NOT NULL AND LENGTH(event_id) = 64
  - valid_sensor_id (drop): not null
  - valid_event_time (drop): not null
  - event_not_ancient (drop): within 7 days
  - rssi_plausible (warn): within plausible dBm range
  - confidence_valid (warn): 0.0–1.0
  - coordinates_paired (warn): both lat/lon present or both null

  Null handling

  - Bronze: all fields nullable except sensor_id + event_time
  - Silver: null fields produce dq_flags array entries (soft flagging)
  - Gold: nulls propagate transparently; alert scoring handles nulls via coalesce

  Malformed record strategy

  - Auto Loader rescuedDataColumn="_rescued_data" captures JSON parse failures
  - A separate observations_bronze_quarantine DLT table captures rescued records
  - Monitor quarantine table volume via Databricks SQL alert: alert if quarantine > 1% of bronze volume

  Schema evolution

  - Auto Loader schemaEvolutionMode=addNewColumns handles new fields from firmware updates
  - New columns appear in bronze automatically
  - Silver schema is explicit (StructType) — new fields land in metadata MAP or require a schema version bump and pipeline code update
  - Schema changes tracked in Unity Catalog lineage automatically

  Replay strategy

  Since bronze is append-only and source files persist in the landing volume:
  1. To replay from source: drop the bronze table contents (if permitted), reset the Auto Loader checkpoint, restart the pipeline
  2. pipelines.reset.allowed=false prevents accidental pipeline reset — requires explicit override
  3. For partial backfill: copy historical files into the landing volume; Auto Loader picks them up on next trigger
  4. Silver and gold can be rebuilt by resetting their pipelines (they read from bronze)

  Lineage and governance

  - Unity Catalog captures column-level lineage for all DLT tables automatically
  - All tables tagged with efence.protocol and quality properties
  - DLT event log (system.lakeflow.pipeline_events) provides full audit trail
  - Use DESCRIBE HISTORY efence.wifi_silver.observations for Delta history audit

  PII / MAC address handling

  ┌───────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │     Layer     │                     Wi-Fi MACs                      │                    BT Addresses                    │
  ├───────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ Bronze        │ Raw — ACL restricted to pipeline SP + security team │ Raw — same ACL                                     │
  ├───────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ Silver        │ SHA-256(normalize(mac) + salt)                      │ SHA-256(normalize(addr) + salt)                    │
  ├───────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ Gold          │ Hashed only                                         │ Hashed only                                        │
  ├───────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
